  "snippet": "Hi Alex, It was great meeting you at the Global Tech Innovators Conference earlier this week—I really enjoyed our discussion on the key technology trends reshaping the industry. As promised, here&#39;s",
  "body": "Hi Alex,\n\nIt was great meeting you at the Global Tech Innovators Conference earlier this week—I really enjoyed our discussion on the key technology trends reshaping the industry.\n\nAs promised, here’s a quick recap of the ideas we touched on and a few resources you might find useful:\n\n1. AI Advancements – Generative AI’s shift from experimentation to production: \n   • McKinsey 2024 State of AI Report (https://www.mckinsey.com/business-functions/mckinsey-digital/our-insights/the-state-of-ai-in-2024).  \n   • OpenAI GPT-4 Technical Paper for deeper model architecture insights.\n\n2. Quantum Computing – Moving from NISQ to fault-tolerant era:\n   • IBM’s roadmap through 2027 (https://research.ibm.com/blog/ibm-quantum-roadmap-2027).  \n   • Boston Consulting Group’s 2023 forecast on quantum value creation.\n\n3. Enterprise Blockchain – Beyond crypto toward supply-chain transparency:\n   • Deloitte 2024 Global Blockchain Survey highlights real-world deployments.  \n   • Hyperledger Foundation case studies.\n\nWould you be open to a quick 30-minute call next week to dig deeper into possible collaboration points? I’m free Tue–Thu between 10 am–1 pm PT, but I can adjust if another time works better for you.\n\nLooking forward to continuing the conversation.\n\nBest regards,\nJane\n"
}","annotations":null}

